SENTINEL Asteroid Belt README
-----------------------------

Welcome to the game Asteroid Belt!
Asteroid Belt is inspired by a MIK CA80 game.
To start the game enter "AB" at the prompt and press ENTER.
The display reads "ASTEROID BELT". Press any key to begin.

You are a space pilot.
You maneuver your ship through an asteroid belt.
You start at the leftmost display position as the "-" character.
Asteroids and asteroid belts fly towards you from the right.
The game is easy to play:
USE the ENTER (fly down) and BACK (fly up) key to dodge all asteroids.
Asteroids always keep getting faster.

Your score is displayed at the rightmost display position.
You are awarded 1 point for dodging an asteroid or asteroid belt.
The score is given in hexadecimal notation.

If an asteroid hits you, the game ends.
The asteroid that hit you, your final score and "GAME OVER" is displayed.
Press ESC to quit the game or any other key to restart.

Enjoy!

